             was indicted for <rs id="t17640728-58-off289" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17640728-58-off289" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17640728-58-off289" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
